version_description: Thanks for using Twenty20! This release includes more bug fixes and user experience improvements.

Thanks for using Twenty20!
The crash while submitting a photo to a challenge has been fixed :)
This releasea also includes more bug fixes and user experience improvements.
Thanks for using Twenty20! This release includes more bug fixes and user experience improvements.

Thanks for using Twenty20! This release features our new Seller Guide which contains everything you need to know to start selling your photos. It is available in the photo selection screen when uploading photos, the sales tab of the activity feed, and in the "Help" settings section of the settings menu. There have also been several bug fixes and improvements in performance and responsiveness.

There have also been several bug fixes (including a recent crash when viewing the actiity feed) and improvements in performance and responsiveness.

Thanks for using Twenty20! This release features our new Seller Guide which contains everything you need to know to start selling your photos. It is available in the photo selection screen when uploading photos, the sales tab of the activity feed, and in the "Help" settings section of the settings menu. There have also been several bug fixes (including a recent crash when viewing the actiity feed and when selecting "See More" in the photo albums list) and improvements in performance and responsiveness.
Thanks for using Twenty20! This release contains many, many bug fixes, performance improvements and udpates for iOS 10.

Thank you for using Twenty20!
Latest Updates:
- Improved the process of submitting photos to the curated collections that customers are searching
- Improved notifications settings
- Bug fixes and user experience improvements

Thank you for using Twenty20!
Latest updates:
-Now it's easier to enter keywords for a photo! When you upload a new photo or edit an existing one, you can choose from one of your recently used keywords.
-Bug fixes and user experience improvements.

Thank you for using Twenty20!
Latest updates:
-New challenge rule: To keep things fair, each photo can now only be entered into a total of three challenges. This will help more people become challenge winners!
-Bug fixes and user experience improvements.

Thank you for using Twenty20!
Latest updates:
-Now introducing photo location as an optional feature: Customers often search for photos by names of location (cities and landmarks) when looking for photos of travel, landscape, and local lifestyle. Add location to help your photos sell better. We fully respect your privacy, so if you choose to include location, you only need to fill out city or landmark names.
-Bug fixes and user experience improvements.

Thank you for using Twenty20!
Latest updates:
- To help your photos sell better, we provide a reminder list of your own photos that need more keywords, based on a calculation of higher possibility to sell. You can find this on your activities feed. (Note: if currently all of your photos have enough keywords, you will not see this list)
- Bug fixes and user experience improvements.

Latest updates:
- We have (finally!) updated our app to support iPhone X and iOS 11
- Show off your status with the coveted Twenty20 Premium blue badge!

Stay tuned for much more to come!

Cha-ching! With this update, we're giving out more prizes in challenges so that you have more chances to win!

In addition to the Grand Prize Winner, each challenge will now award Editor's Picks. Grand Prize Winners win the full listed prize amount ($100, $150, or $200). Each Editor's Pick will receive a smaller cash prize by also splitting an equal-sized prize amount (ex. if 10 Editor's Picks split $200 each winner gets $20).
